_sText:
this is another halo 1 deathmatch remake.
this is a small map so I have incorperated a new method of entering the map, to provide a deathmatch type spawning without actually having the deathmatch mod.

of course it should be perfect for css dm aswell.
IMPORTANT
the gravity must be set at halo equivelent for this map to play right.
type
"sv_gravity 640"
into the console without the speachmarks.
